der and measure the fluorescence according to the following parameters:<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Excitation \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0   \u00a0 \u00a0 ~480 nm<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Emission \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0   ~520 nm<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Integration time\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0     40 s<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Lag time\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 0 s<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Gain\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Optimal<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Number of flashes\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0 10<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Calculated well\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 highest standard<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Shaking \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0  5 s<\/div><\/div>"}},{"id":1054725,"guid":"6DD8C770743A11EA9C74E99F67203752","order_id":2,"type_id":28,"title":"equipment","source":{"brand":"Tecan","sku":"TEC006436I","specifications":null,"can_edit":false,"name":"Infinite M Nano","type":"Absorbance plate reader","link":"https:\/\/lifesciences.tecan.com\/plate_readers\/fluorescence_absorbance_luminescence?p=tab--2","file":null,"image":null}},{"id":1054726,"guid":"735ADEAB7F9F4D8FB9853A715DFA0A10","order_id":3,"type_id":26,"title":"notes","source":{"id":0,"parent_id":0,"uri":"","title":"","body":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\">It is also possible to set the gain to a fixed value (e.g. 100). If the fluorescence values of the standard drop over time this could indicate damage to the reagents or the RNA standard.<\/div><\/div>","created_on":0,"ch